OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783792086
OL,3,CFormer news presenter Dermot Murnaghan
OL,4,Chas died aged 68
OL,6,FFormer news presenter Dermot Murnaghan
OL,7,Fhas died aged 68, a year after he
OL,8,Frevealed he had been diagnosed with
OL,9,Fstage four prostate cancer.
OL,11,FThe former BBC, ITV and Sky News
OL,12,Fjournalist died "peacefully" on
OL,13,FSaturday "following a period of
OL,14,Fillness with prostate cancer", his
OL,15,Ffamily said in a statement.
OL,17,FThe media personality was a long-term
OL,18,Fnews presenter, best known for his 15-
OL,19,Fyear tenure as a lead anchor for Sky
OL,20,FNews.
OL,26,@uD@JOUvD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
