OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783792086
OL,3,CFormer news presenter Dermot Murnaghan
OL,4,Chas died aged 68
OL,6,FHe also presented the news for Channel
OL,7,F4, as well as flagship programmes such
OL,8,Fas the ITV Evening News and the BBC
OL,9,FNews at Six and Ten during his career
OL,10,Fas a journalist and broadcaster.
OL,12,FMurnaghan's family released the
OL,13,Fstatement on one of his social media
OL,14,Faccounts:
OL,16,FThe statement continued: "The family
OL,17,Fwish to thank the medical teams who
OL,18,Fcared for Dermot with such sensitivity
OL,19,Fand extraordinary compassion
OL,20,Fthroughout his illness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783792086
OL,3,CFormer news presenter Dermot Murnaghan
OL,4,Chas died aged 68
OL,6,F"Also, for the many, many kind
OL,7,Fmessages of goodwill that he received
OL,8,Fover the last year since his diagnosis
OL,9,Fof Stage IV prostate cancer and his
OL,10,Fsubsequent campaigning to raise
OL,11,Fawareness for screening programmes for
OL,12,Fthe disease.
OL,14,F"In accordance with his wishes, the
OL,15,Ffuneral will be a small family
OL,16,Fceremony. A memorial service for
OL,17,Ffriends and colleagues will follow at
OL,18,FSt Bride's Church, Fleet Street (the
OL,19,FJournalists' Church) later this year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783792086
OL,3,CFormer news presenter Dermot Murnaghan
OL,4,Chas died aged 68
OL,6,F"The family request that anyone
OL,7,Fwishing to remember him considers
OL,8,Fsupporting Prostate Cancer UK,
OL,9,FProstate Cancer Research and North
OL,10,FLondon Hospice so that others may
OL,11,Fbenefit from the research and care he
OL,12,Freceived."
OL,14,FMurnaghan had also used social media
OL,15,Fto announce his diagnosis in June 2025.
OL,17,FHe wrote: "Some personal
OL,18,Fnews......I've been diagnosed with
OL,19,FStage IV advanced prostate cancer."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
