PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783792086
OL,3,CFormer news presenter Dermot Murnaghan
OL,4,Chas died aged 68
OL,6,FHe added that he was responding well
OL,7,Fto treatment and was "blessed to be
OL,8,Ffortified by the monumental love and
OL,9,Fsupport of my wife, family and close
OL,10,Ffriends."
OL,12,FHe used his position to encourage men
OL,13,Fover 50 to seek early screening and
OL,14,Finterviewed Sir Cliff Richard, as he
OL,15,Frevealed his own diagnosis with
OL,16,Fprostate cancer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
