OL,3,CFormer news presenter Dermot Murnaghan
OL,4,Chas died aged 68
OL,6,FIn the frenetic world of TV News,
OL,7,FDermot Murnaghan was the calm in the
OL,8,Feye of the storm. Unflappable,
OL,9,Fprofessional and above all trusted by
OL,10,Fviewers and colleagues to always
OL,11,Fdeliver.
OL,13,FHis warmth, easy going style and
OL,14,Fauthority as a broadcaster shone out
OL,15,Fon all the UK's major TV networks for
OL,16,Fmore than four decades.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783792086
OL,3,CFormer news presenter Dermot Murnaghan
OL,4,Chas died aged 68
OL,6,FAfter starting his career with Channel
OL,7,F4 he went on to become one of the main
OL,8,Fpresenters on ITV News. And it was
OL,9,Fhere, where, in 1997, he announced the
OL,10,Fdeath of Princess Diana in a car crash
OL,11,Fin Paris.
OL,13,FIn his time at ITN, he presented
OL,14,Fcoverage of many other major stories,
OL,15,Fincluding the handover of Hong Kong,
OL,16,Fthe funeral of the Queen Mother and
OL,17,Fthe 9/11 attacks in the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783792086
OL,3,CFormer news presenter Dermot Murnaghan
OL,4,Chas died aged 68
OL,6,FMurnaghan's formidable skill earned
OL,7,Fhim a coveted Royal Television Society
OL,8,Faward. He later also won the
OL,9,Fprestigious Newscaster of the Year
OL,10,Faward, from the Television & Radio
OL,11,FIndustries Club.
OL,13,FDuring his time at the BBC, he spent
OL,14,Ffive years presenting the
OL,15,Fbroadcaster's Breakfast programme as
OL,16,Fwell as its Six and Ten o'clock
OL,17,Fbulletins. He also fronted the quiz
OL,18,Fshow Eggheads for more than a decade.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
