OL,3,CFormer news presenter Dermot Murnaghan
OL,4,Chas died aged 68
OL,6,FHe was known as a consummate
OL,7,Fprofessional with the sure touch who
OL,8,Fembodied that most valued of qualities
OL,9,F- Trust.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
